==setup.rake

This is a simple rake task to install whatever plugins you most frequently use in your rails apps.
So far, it just installs shoulda and some other plugins related to shoulda.

=Usage

Copy the setup.rake file to the lib/tasks directory of your rails app. You should then be able to 
run any tasks in the file from the root directory of your app.

=Included tasks

rake setup:plugins:all           # Run all plugin tasks
rake setup:plugins:jrails        # Install jRails
rake setup:plugins:restful_auth  # Install RESTful Authentication
rake setup:plugins:shoulda       # Install Shoulda, shoulda_generator, and Factory Girl
